{"id":597325,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/10/【网络民议】语录的前奏/","date":"2018-10-09T19:50:35Z","modified":"2018-10-10T06:05:35Z","title":"【网络民议】语录的前奏","content":"<p>编者按：据新华社消息，由中共中央宣传部、中央广播电视总台联合创作的《百家讲坛》特别节目《平“语”近人——习近平总书记用典》，于8日至19日在央视综合频道晚间播出。节目从习近平一系列重要讲话、文章、谈话中所引用的古代典籍和经典名句为切入点，旨在推动习近平新时代中国特色社会主义思想的生动阐释与广泛传播。在第一集播出后，网民评论：准备过桥过路要背语录了</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-597326\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/Image-from-iOS-8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"315\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-597327\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/Image-from-iOS-1-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"323\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/Image-from-iOS-1-2.jpg 2758w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/Image-from-iOS-1-2-300x194.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/Image-from-iOS-1-2-768x497.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/Image-from-iOS-1-2-1024x662.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/Image-from-iOS-1-2-230x150.jpg 230w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-597328\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/Image-from-iOS-2-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/Image-from-iOS-2-1.jpg 1440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/Image-from-iOS-2-1-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/Image-from-iOS-2-1-768x576.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/Image-from-iOS-2-1-1024x768.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>以下评论由中国数字时代编辑收集自网络：</strong></p>\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"https://weibo.com/5472960171\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">一念解空居士</a>：语录的前奏</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://weibo.com/2162337833\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"n